OL,3,CGovernment plans to challenge court
OL,4,Cruling over Sean Brown public inquiry
OL,6,FThe government is to challenge a court
OL,7,Fruling that found its refusal to hold
OL,8,Fa public inquiry into the killing of a
OL,9,FGAA official was 'unlawful'.
OL,11,FAt the start of April, Belfast's Court
OL,12,Fof Appeal had given Northern Ireland
OL,13,FSecretary of State four weeks to
OL,14,Freconsider a decision not to hold an
OL,15,Finquiry into the murder of Sean Brown
OL,16,Fin 1997 by the Loyalist Volunteer
OL,17,FForce.
OL,19,FFriday was the deadline day to make a
OL,20,Fdecision.
