OL,6,FMr Benn has not confirmed he will
OL,7,Fultimately take the case to the
OL,8,FSupreme Court, but has applied for
OL,9,F"protective leave" to appeal to the
OL,10,FUK's highest court if he believes that
OL,11,Fcourse of action to be "necessary".
OL,13,FFirst Minister Michelle O'Neill said
OL,14,Fthe decision taken is "a cruel and
OL,15,Finhumane act" and "the latest example
OL,16,Fof British government political
OL,17,Fcynicism."
