OL,6,F"I am taking steps to repeal and
OL,7,Freplace the previous government's
OL,8,FLegacy Act to ensure that we have a
OL,9,Flegacy system that is capable of
OL,10,Fdelivering for all families who lost
OL,11,Floved ones during the Troubles, and
OL,12,Fwho are seeking answers.
OL,14,FHe continued: "It is clear that the
OL,15,Fdetailed judgement requires a full and
OL,16,Fconsidered response. I have therefore
OL,17,Ftoday asked the Court of Appeal for
OL,18,Fmore time to consider it and the terms
OL,19,Fof the declaration.
