OL,6,F"This will allow me to receive
OL,7,Fcomprehensive advice that responds in
OL,8,Ffull to the issues the Court has
OL,9,Fidentified.
OL,11,F"Also, given the approaching deadline
OL,12,Ffrom the Court for requesting leave to
OL,13,Fappeal, I have today asked the Court
OL,14,Ffor leave to appeal to the Supreme
OL,15,FCourt, in case that should ultimately
OL,16,Fbe necessary.
