OL,6,F"It is an affront to the basic
OL,7,Fprinciples of truth and justice that
OL,8,FKeir Starmer's government is
OL,9,Fthreatening to once again drag Bridie
OL,10,FBrown and her family back to court.
OL,12,F"As Bridie Brown previously said, five
OL,13,FHigh Court judges have instructed the
OL,14,FBritish government to do the right
OL,15,Fthing, yet it seems hellbent on
OL,16,Fdenying her family a public inquiry.
