OL,6,F"This cruel and inhumane act is just
OL,7,Fthe latest example of British
OL,8,Fgovernment political cynicism `
OL,9,Fblocking the right of families to
OL,10,Faccess truth and justice.
OL,12,F"This will only add further insult to
OL,13,Fthe Brown family who, unlike the
OL,14,FBritish government, have led with
OL,15,Fcourage and dignity in their fight for
OL,16,Fanswers into Sean Brown's murder.
OL,18,F"These cruel actions undermine public
OL,19,Fconfidence in the administration of
OL,20,Fjustice.
